Using `h : volume A = 0`:
`ℙ (A ∩ B) / ℙ B = 0 * (ℙ (B ∩ A) / ℙ A) / ℙ B`.
`ℙ (A ∩ B) / ℙ B = 0`.
This is true because `A` has measure 0, so `A ∩ B` has measure 0.

